mpb
------------------------------------------
MPB is a free software package for computing photonic band structures and
modes.

Runtime requirements:
  bash-5.2.21-1
  cygwin-3.6.0-0.203.gf78009cb1ccf
  libctl7-4.5.1-1bl2
  libfftw3-devel-3.3.10-1
  libfftw3_3-3.3.10-1
  libguile3.0_1-3.0.9-3
  libhdf5_200-1.12.3-1
  liblapack0-3.12.0-1
  libmpb-devel-1.11.1-1bl2
  libmpb1-1.11.1-1bl2
  libnlopt0-2.8.0-1bl1
  libopenblas-0.3.26-1
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  autoconf-archive-2023.02.20-1
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libctl-devel-4.5.1-1bl2
  libfftw3-devel-3.3.10-1
  libguile3.0-devel-3.0.9-3
  libhdf5-devel-1.12.3-1
  liblapack-devel-3.12.0-1
  libnlopt-devel-2.8.0-1bl1
  libtool-2.5.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/NanoComp/mpb

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/NanoComp/mpb/archive/refs/tags/v1.11.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack mpb-1.11.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./mpb-1.11.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mpb-1.11.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/mpb-1.11.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmpb1-1.11.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmpb-devel-1.11.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(mpb)
  /usr/bin/mpb-data.exe
  /usr/bin/mpb-split
  /usr/bin/mpb.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/mpb.README
  /usr/share/doc/mpb/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/mpb/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/mpb/COPYRIGHT
  /usr/share/doc/mpb/NEWS.md
  /usr/share/doc/mpb/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/mpb/TODO
  /usr/share/man/man1/mpb-data.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/mpb-split.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/mpb.1.gz
  /usr/share/mpb/mpb.scm

(libmpb1)
  /usr/bin/cygmpb-1.dll

(libmpb-devel)
  /usr/include/mpb.h
  /usr/include/mpb/eigensolver.h
  /usr/include/mpb/matrices.h
  /usr/include/mpb/maxwell.h
  /usr/include/mpb/scalar.h
  /usr/include/mpb/verbosity.h
  /usr/lib/libmpb.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/mpb.pc

